{"tid":903413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港資裁8千人】iPhone芒惠州廠爆4日工潮 驚動防暴警維穩","createTime":"2018-11-15T13:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T16:23:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":124,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"074679402d20bbcdd9a4d6a08f22da18f9bccfdd","tid":903413,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181115/large/1542285148_5e81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181115%2Flarge%2F1542285148_5e81.jpg&h=609607f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果手機iPhone訂單驟減，港資私人企業、全球手機屏幕生產商「伯恩光學」廣東惠州廠區近日突然宣佈大裁員，網傳11月初開始先後裁減5,000和3,000名工人，9日至12日連續爆發大規模工潮。據報，因接近年底裁員，被裁工人較難再找到工作，也不滿意公司的賠償條件，遂紛紛圍堵工廠門口抗議，引發防暴特警出動維穩。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在微信寫道：「惠州伯恩一天辭掉5,000名臨時工，富士康雙休沒班加，作為一名常年打工的我，心裏面感覺很涼。以後失業了怎麼辦，沒班加了怎麼辦？一個月拿2,000的底薪怎麼養家。」<br />\n<br />\n微信群組「伯恩光學派遣員工」亦發出了通知：「惠州伯恩光學5,000人被炒，防暴警察現場維護秩序！有工作的人千萬別隨意跳槽！今年中美貿易戰，出口訂單不如以往，加上實習生寒假生已經陸陸續續到崗，勞務市場已接近飽和，有工作的就好好珍惜吧！」<br />\n<br />\n為三星、蘋果、小米、VIVO等品牌手機生產屏幕的伯恩光學有限公司，成立於1986年，為港資私人企業。原為富士光學有限公司及伯恩光學有限公司，至2010年，為達到更高的管理及生產效益，正式整合為伯恩光學有限公司。至今，工業園的廠房面積已達850,000平方米，技術與產能的結合，令伯恩成為目前全球最大的玻璃面板生產商，全球市場佔有率超過60%。深圳和惠州兩大生產基地的全年生產總值高達300億元人民幣（約338億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181115/58918089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181115%2F58918089&d=ZM%2FYmqnHOnhqe5jVT8WB9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6e303932\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181115%2F58918089&h=c02cba5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181115/58918089</a>"},{"pid":"8aedd7f5695ceabdc2b9640fce31c6fd4f2464a5","tid":903413,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab9888f564c5aa339e80c21622c1f7de349433f7","tid":903413,"uid":55533,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"2382會唔會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5911bbb5bd3820b785195e0a321573b50a3803","tid":903413,"uid":511,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"惠州伯恩一天辭掉5,000名臨時工<br />\n<br />\n臨時都唔裁得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fa90ed477eb88bbf5f4f08518846ce71b10a39","tid":903413,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5790d885d8f6f9aa3bbabc4f4600d422e47636","tid":903413,"uid":121146,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒  回鄉創業姐"},{"pid":"7e5dd737e75ebf4a6a0dcabf24f494877c8d70d5","tid":903413,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:04:45.000Z","msg":"分批炒會唔會好d"},{"pid":"44b994541b8240f4ff0d216de5dd50a1cc762fe5","tid":903413,"uid":52215,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:06:01.000Z","msg":"以前岩岩畢業2003年去富士光學橫崗間廠做人事，仲識當時楊老板，冇諗過宜家楊老板變香港十大富豪之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6cd0fdb254515fcd1e9179b3ff15a504523856","tid":903413,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e5dd737e75ebf4a6a0dcabf24f494877c8d70d5","tid":903413,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:04:45.000Z","msg":"分批炒會唔會好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"無單  留黎都無用"},{"pid":"557d849ac7f2b324574c074fdecd9f0edd15f7c5","tid":903413,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"想幫手疏導下春運啫<br />\n提早返鄉啫"},{"pid":"33b228c7b493a1caa64f57dc5df3db0414172603","tid":903413,"uid":5127